## Answer 5 — Highest Order Amount Per Month
WITH ranked AS (
SELECT *,
       ROW_NUMBER() OVER(
           PARTITION BY DATE_FORMAT(order_date, '%Y-%m')
           ORDER BY amount DESC
       ) rn
FROM Orders
)
SELECT order_id, order_date, amount
FROM ranked
WHERE rn = 1;
```

